# Z3R Simulator Reborn - Project Context

## Overview
This is a fork of the Z3R Simulator (Zelda: A Link to the Past Randomizer Simulator). The original source was deobfuscated from the production Angular 4 bundle by [eclectic-sh/z3rsim-deobfuscated](https://github.com/eclectic-sh/z3rsim-deobfuscated). This fork adds offline functionality including spoiler log loading and seed generation.

## Key Repos
- **Origin (your fork)**: `https://github.com/DerpaholicRex/z3rsim-reborn.git`
- **Upstream (deobfuscated source)**: `https://github.com/eclectic-sh/z3rsim-deobfuscated.git`

## Tech Stack
- **Angular 14.2.0**
- **TypeScript 4.7.4**
- **Angular CLI 14.2.0**
- **Node 16/18+**
- **Bootstrap 3.3.7** via ngx-bootstrap 5.6.2
- **jQuery 3.3.1** (loaded globally in index.html)

## Project Structure
```
deobfuscated/
├── src/                          # Angular app source
│   ├── index.html                # App shell (compiled by Angular CLI)
│   ├── main.ts                   # Bootstrap entry
│   ├── app.module.ts             # NgModule
│   ├── app-routing.module.ts     # Routes
│   ├── components/               # ~18 components (.ts + .html + .css each)
│   ├── services/                 # Injectable services
│   ├── models/                   # TypeScript models/enums
│   ├── dungeons/                 # 15 dungeon setup files
│   └── data/                     # Light/Dark world location tables
├── scripts/                      # Helper scripts (loaded as-is)
├── assets/                       # PNGs (item/dungeon/map icons)
├── hotfix/                       # JSON data (item maps, location maps, spoiler log)
├── fonts/                        # Font Awesome + Hammersmith One
├── dist/                         # Build output (served by GitHub Pages)
├── angular.json                  # Build config
├── .github/workflows/deploy.yml  # GitHub Actions: builds and deploys to Pages
├── 404.html                      # SPA redirect for GitHub Pages
├── runSite.bat                   # Windows convenience script
└── runSite.sh                    # Unix convenience script
```

## How Seed Loading Works (Critical)
The app uses a **pre-2019 ALttPR seed format**. Current alttpr.com seeds won't load natively.

1. **integration.js** handles spoiler log loading:
   - User clicks "Load Spoiler Log" → file picker → parses JSON
   - Calls `window.saveSpoilerLogToLocalStorage(spoilerLogData)` to save the log
   - Calls `window.loadAndGenerateItemArray()` → generates item array
   - Saves `seedHash` and `itemArray` to localStorage
   - Reloads the page
   
2. After reload, **SeedService.getSeed()** reads from localStorage:
   - `localStorage.getItem('seedHash')` → seed identifier
   - `localStorage.getItem('itemArray')` → item placement data
   - `localStorage.getItem('seedMetadataPrefix')` → metadata prefix
   - Returns a fakeObservable that provides seedData.data = prefix + itemArray
   
3. **Generate Seed** uses `https://api.allorigins.win/raw?url=` as a CORS proxy to call `https://alttpr.com/api/randomizer`, then follows the same save + reload flow.

## Building
```bash
npm install
npm run build                 # Outputs to dist/
```

## GitHub Pages
- **URL**: `https://derpaholicrex.github.io/z3rsim-reborn/`
- **Deploy**: Automated via GitHub Actions on push to `main`

## Running Locally
```bash
npm run serve:dist
# Open http://localhost:8000
```

## Remotes
- `origin` → `https://github.com/DerpaholicRex/z3rsim-reborn.git`
- `deobfuscated` → `https://github.com/eclectic-sh/z3rsim-deobfuscated.git`

## Key Caveats
- The seed format is pre-2019 ALttPR - current seeds from alttpr.com will NOT load
- A bundled default seed is included in hotfix/ so the app can be demonstrated
- The app uses `HttpClient` (upgraded from deprecated `@angular/http`)
